propel.core.tracing

Class Stopwatch

  • java.lang.Object
    • propel.core.tracing.Stopwatch

  • public class Stopwatch
extends java.lang.Object
    High-precision stop watch class for measuring time taken to execute some code. This is not a thread-safe class.
